{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"381","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"過期先別丟！英國發明「觸覺標籤」　一摸就知道食物狀態","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>為了保障食品安全，廠商大多會把保存期限訂得比較保守，有些食物可能剛過期但依然新鮮，這時如果被丟掉就會變成浪費。因此英國一間新創公司發明了「觸覺標籤」，讓消費者摸一下就能知道食物狀態。</p>\n\n<div class='fb-quote fb_iframe_widget' fb-iframe-plugin-query='app_id=146858218737386&amp;container_width=1349&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181109%2F1301428.htm&amp;locale=zh_TW&amp;sdk=joey' fb-xfbml-state='rendered' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: inline-block; position: absolute; left: 327.5px; top: 1084px;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>據Techable報導，有調查顯示，全球每年約有13噸食物會被浪費，其中有很多都是剛超過保存期限就被丟棄的食品，英國新創公司Minica就發明了「Mimica Touch」智慧標籤，採用明膠對每種食物個別製作。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'><img alt='▲▼英國新創公司發明智慧標籤，可以辨別食物新鮮度。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Solveiga Pakštaitė）' border='1' height='387' src='https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3679/3679047.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; background: transparent; max-width: 650px; height: auto;' width='600' /></p>\n\n<div class='fb-quote fb_iframe_widget' fb-iframe-plugin-query='app_id=146858218737386&amp;container_width=1349&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181109%2F1301428.htm&amp;locale=zh_TW&amp;sdk=joey' fb-xfbml-state='rendered' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: inline-block; position: absolute; left: 217.5px; top: 1314px;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'><strong style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;'>▲老年人可能看不清楚包裝上文字，用摸的最快速。</strong></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>標籤分成左右兩部分，右半邊會隨著食物狀態改變，如果摸起來很平滑，代表食物依然很新鮮，若凹凸不平則是已經腐壞；而左半邊是永遠呈現平滑狀態的對照組。</p>\n\n<div class='fb-quote fb_iframe_widget' fb-iframe-plugin-query='app_id=146858218737386&amp;container_width=1349&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181109%2F1301428.htm&amp;locale=zh_TW&amp;sdk=joey' fb-xfbml-state='rendered' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: inline-block; position: absolute; left: 329px; top: 1811px;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>貼上這個標籤，就能快速得知食物是否過期，減少食物浪費疑慮，也能讓老年人、視障者更方便判斷，是一種無障礙設計。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>Minica公司今年3月已經開始和牛奶廠商合作，以盒裝牛奶為第一個測試對象，未來有望應用在更多食品上。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>英國近幾年越來越重視食物浪費議題，連鎖超市特易購（Tesco）上月就發聲明表示，未來將會有116項蔬果不在標示賞味期限。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>事實上，特易購早在5月就對70項生鮮蔬果實施這個計畫，包括蘋果、馬鈴薯、番茄、檸檬以及洋蔥等等。食品廢棄物部門負責人里特（Mark Little）表示，有些客戶搞不清楚食物「最佳賞味期限」與「保存期限」的不同，導致有些還能吃的食物被丟棄，其中又以蔬果最容易被浪費。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>特易購目前也正在與供應商合作，努力將原本可能浪費的食物創造成新產品。例如，把超過賞味期限，但完全沒有食安問題的酪梨，送往供應商製成酪梨醬，再賣給消費者，減少消費者丟棄新鮮的食物這類情形。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Meiryo UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.7;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>資料來源:https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181109/1301428.htm</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-11-22","clk_count":"181"}},"__N_SSG":true}